title: Tenant Identity Verification
description: Verify tenant identity through official Home Affairs DHA database. Confirms identity documents are authentic and match government records. Fast digital verification process.

title: Home Affairs DHA Identity Verification
description: Official identity verification through Department of Home Affairs. Validates South African ID numbers and documents against government database. Prevents identity fraud.

title: Tenant Credit Profile
description: Quick credit overview showing payment behavior and credit score. Identifies payment patterns and financial responsibility. Essential for rental decisions.

title: Detailed Credit Report
description: Comprehensive credit report with full payment history. Shows all credit accounts debts and judgments. Bureau-verified financial information.

title: Rental Payment Profile
description: Track record of rental payments from previous landlords. Shows payment punctuality and rental history. Critical for assessing tenant reliability.

title: Landlord Reference Verification
description: Direct verification with previous landlords. Confirms rental history behavior and disputes. Professional reference checking service.

title: Employment Verification
description: Confirm current employment status and position. Verifies employer details and job tenure. Protects against employment fraud.

title: Income & Affordability Assessment
description: Detailed income verification and affordability analysis. Calculates debt-to-income ratio. Ensures tenant can afford rent payments.

title: Criminal Record Check
description: Consent-based criminal record screening. Searches national criminal database. Identifies potential safety risks for properties.

title: Fraud & Risk Flags Screening
description: Comprehensive fraud database screening. Identifies known fraud patterns and red flags. Multi-bureau risk assessment.

title: Essential Tenant Check
description: Basic tenant screening bundle. Includes identity verification credit profile and fraud screening. Perfect for budget-conscious landlords.

title: Standard Tenant Screening
description: Popular complete screening package. Includes identity credit rental history and employment verification. Most comprehensive value.

title: Comprehensive Tenant Vetting
description: Premium full-spectrum tenant vetting. All checks included plus criminal record and detailed reports. Maximum protection for high-value properties.
